Package: alt3code
Title: Packaged R Source Code for Updating the alt-3.uk Website
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Firth", email = "footymath@alt-3.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package collects together, with rudimentary documentation, all of 
    the R functions that are used to populate the public website at alt-3.uk.  
    Included are functions to download match results, to process them into an
    "alt-3" league table, and to produce a table formatted for the web.  
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
